{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"keyfileSettingsBackendNew"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"filename"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"rootPath"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"rootGroup"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">? = nil) -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsBackendRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO18SettingsBackendRefV","text":"SettingsBackendRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The filename of the keyfile to use is given by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"filename"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All settings read to or written from the backend must fall under the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path given in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":" (which must start and end with a slash and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"not contain two consecutive slashes).  "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":" may be “\/”."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootGroup"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" then it specifies the name of the keyfile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group used for keys that are written directly below "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":".  For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":" is “\/apps\/example\/” and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootGroup"},{"type":"text","text":" is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“toplevel”, then settings the key “\/apps\/example\/enabled” to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" will cause the following to appear in the keyfile:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["  [toplevel]","  enabled=true"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootGroup"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" then it is not permitted to store keys"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly below the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For keys not stored directly below "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":" (ie: in a sub-path),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the name of the subpath (with the final slash stripped) is used as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the name of the keyfile group.  To continue the example, if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“\/apps\/example\/profiles\/default\/font-size” were set to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"12 then the following would appear in the keyfile:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["  [profiles\/default]","  font-size=12"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The backend will refuse writes (and return writability as being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":") for keys outside of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":" and, in the event that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootGroup"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", also for keys directly under "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rootPath"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Writes will also be refused if the backend detects that it has the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inability to rewrite the keyfile (ie: the containing directory is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"writable)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There is no checking done for your key namespace clashing with the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"syntax of the key file format.  For example, if you have ‘[’ or ‘]’"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"characters in your path names or ‘=’ in your key names you may be in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"trouble."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The backend reads default values from a keyfile called "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"defaults"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the directory specified by the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GKeyfileSettingsBackend:defaults-dir"},{"type":"text","text":" property,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and a list of locked keys from a text file with the name "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"locks"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the same location."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/keyfilesettingsbackendnew(filename:rootpath:rootgroup:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/keyfileSettingsBackendNew(filename:rootPath:rootGroup:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates a keyfile-backed "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsBackend"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"keyfileSettingsBackendNew"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"filename"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"rootPath"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"rootGroup"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">?) -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SettingsBackendRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO18SettingsBackendRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"title":"keyfileSettingsBackendNew(filename:rootPath:rootGroup:)","roleHeading":"Function","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func","externalI